QuestData.Title: Jungleweb Infestation
QuestData.Description:
The walls of the temple could provide us with vital protection against the naga, but the temple is overrun with jungle spiders.
We'll need to clear out the infestation before the tribe can take refuge at the temple.
Venture into the lower ruins and lay waste to the spiders that have nested there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay $1oa Jungleweb Crawlers and $2oa Jungleweb Hatchlings.
